{
  "stem": "22944.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "During the day-- This is the information that we received from the neighbors, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] who said that, obviously, why they didn't help him-- sorry-- why they didn't help him to be saved or rescued, that I would not know.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the thing is we found out after the war that during the day, he went out in the fields [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and was hiding wherever he could.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nighttime, he was coming back to the cottage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all he got was some bread and coffee.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he was, of course, sleeping overnight.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The next day was going out again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And this proceeding was lasting for a long time, because he just probably was praying, hoping for some kind of help from somebody what didn't come.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Eventually-- that must be the second month, something, during that-- the summer was still on, but I think, probably some time later, he must have-- somebody informed about him.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some Germans or the Hlinka army came in, and they must have been tipped off.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They came in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he probably must have seen them coming-- spilled the coffee out, but the kettle apparently was still warm.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So they realized he couldn't got very far.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They tried looking for it-- for him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we had very large eiderdown.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Apparently, he was hiding near the mattress, under the mattress, but they found him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they just tied him up like a pig and just-- by foot, And they took him out to the car or van, whatever was outside.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he was taken down to one of the transports.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Was taken to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And a story we got from somebody who met him on the way was, he was still a gentleman, what he was.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
